      "title": "The friend became immortal by sitting on the house beam",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Jaffna - A person who came to his friend's house in Tirunelveli area and sat on a chair suddenly fainted and collapsed.",
        "Jaffna - Balasubramaniam Iyer Gananathasarma (age 34) of Koppai has died.",
        "The family immediately rushed him to the hospital, but the doctors declared him already dead. (R)"
